SPINACH CHEESE BLEND: LOW MOISTURE WHOLE MILK MOZZARELLA (PASTEURIZED MILK, CHEESE CULTURES, SALT, ENZYMES), POWDERED CELLULOSE (TO PREVENT CAKING), SPINACH, IMPORTED PARMESAN CHEESE (MADE FROM PASTEURIZED PART SKIM COW'S MILK, CULTURE, SALT, CORN STARCH, AND POWDERED CELLULOSE TO PREVENT CAKING, IMPORTED ROMANO CHEESE (SHEEP'S MILK, CHEESE, CULTURE, SALT, ENZYMES), POWDERED CELLULOSE TO PREVENT CAKING, CALCIUM PROPIONATE.
